[Method]
Navigate
[Prefix]
Odcl_Html_
[Desc]
This method will force the HtmlControl to navigate to a URL or directory.  For example ôwww.objectdcl.comö or ôc:\\tempö
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName
\par\tab Destination
[as String]

[Method]
Stop
[Prefix]
Odcl_Html_
[Desc]
This method forces the HtmlControl to stop its current activity.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName

[Method]
Refresh
[Prefix]
Odcl_Html_
[Desc]
This method forces the HtmlControl to reload the current file.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName


[Method]
GoBack
[Prefix]
Odcl_Html_
[Desc]
This method forces the HtmlControl to go back to its previously selected file.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName


[Method]
GoHome
[Prefix]
Odcl_Html_
[Desc]
This method forces the HtmlControl to go to the systemĺs selected home URL page.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName



[Method]
GoSearch
[Prefix]
Odcl_Html_
[Desc]
This method forces the HtmlControl to go to the systemĺs selected search page.
